OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,FWarning: Some readers may find details
OL,7,Fin this article distressing
OL,9,FThe father of a teenager jailed for
OL,10,Fattempting to behead a Kurdish barber
OL,11,Fafter becoming radicalised by the far
OL,12,Fright has accused the police and
OL,13,Fmental health services of failing his
OL,14,Fdaughter.
OL,16,FAlina Burns was jailed for more than
OL,17,F15 years last month after attacking
OL,18,FMohammed Mahmoodi, 27, with an axe in
OL,19,FBristol.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
