FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,FHer father, Luke, 52, said his
OL,7,Fdaughter had been let down by several
OL,8,Fagencies and expressed frustration
OL,9,Fpolice had not told him about her
OL,10,Fradicalisation.
OL,12,F"I think we just feel very guilty that
OL,13,Fthis had happened, that we had failed
OL,14,Fher," he said.
OL,16,F"But in the back of our minds it's not
OL,17,Fjust we failed her. Everyone failed
OL,18,Fher.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@EO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,F"You go back to the police, you go
OL,7,Fback to CAMHS, you go back to hospital
OL,8,Feducation, you go back to the school,
OL,9,Fyou go back all the way back.
OL,11,F"Everyone failed her. She wanted a
OL,12,Fpurpose in life, but she was denied
OL,13,Fit. She was not able to do GCSEs, she
OL,14,Fwas not able to have a future.
OL,16,F"It is devastating."
OL,18,FBurns is autistic and has anorexia and
OL,19,Fwhen she was younger was involved with
OL,20,FChild and Adolescent Mental Health
OL,21,FServices (CAMHS).
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOUxD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,F"Different organisations were involved
OL,7,Fwhen going back to the homelessness
OL,8,Fperiod of time, but there was not
OL,9,Fenough support for Alina in school,"
OL,10,Fhe said.
OL,12,F"Once it was decided by CAMHS that she
OL,13,Fwas too unwell to attend school and
OL,14,Fthen due to a miscommunication between
OL,15,Fthe school, Bristol City Council and
OL,16,Fhospital education, no referral was
OL,17,Fever made.
OL,19,F"She was literally abandoned."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@dO]tD@AOU{D@AOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
