PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,FThe 19-year-old had been radicalised
OL,7,Fby neo-Nazi extremism and had been in
OL,8,Fcontact with far-right groups.
OL,10,FIn an interview with the Press
OL,11,FAssociation, Mr Burns warned other
OL,12,Fparents of the dangers that isolated
OL,13,Fand vulnerable young people, such as
OL,14,Fhis daughter, faced while online.
OL,16,F"It was not something she was
OL,17,Fexplaining to us, so it must have been
OL,18,Fextremely quick simply because she had
OL,19,Fonly had the laptop for a number of
OL,20,Fmonths," he said.
OL,26,@xD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,F"Before May she had expressed a few
OL,7,Fviews, which were very Reform-type
OL,8,Fviews, to us. But nothing more than
OL,9,Fthat.
OL,11,F"It was not as if she was openly
OL,12,Fstating views that were controversial.
OL,13,FThere was nothing of concern. She had
OL,14,Fnever had any violent tendencies.
OL,16,F"There was no concern at all that she
OL,17,Fwould be aggressive or violent to
OL,18,Fanybody. That was completely out of
OL,19,Fcharacter and completely unacceptable.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,F"The attack was shocking and we are
OL,7,Fshocked that it happened and were just
OL,8,Fvery grateful that the victim was not
OL,9,Finjured in a physical sense more than
OL,10,Fwhat he was.
OL,12,F"She was absolutely lovely at home,
OL,13,Fshe was lovely with her brother who
OL,14,Fhas severe disabilities.
OL,16,F"There was never a concern, there was
OL,17,Fnothing to raise suspicion."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOUyD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,FThe family only later learned that
OL,7,Fconcerns had been raised about the
OL,8,Fteenager months before the attack,
OL,9,Fwhen she told an older man she had met
OL,10,Fon a dating site to "kill all Jews and
OL,11,FMuslims".
OL,13,FAvon and Somerset Police referred the
OL,14,Freport to Counter Terrorism Policing,
OL,15,Fwhich concluded it did not meet the
OL,16,Fthreshold for an investigation.
OL,26,@rD@UOUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,FMr Burns said he was "furious" after
OL,7,Flearning from news reports following
OL,8,Fhis daughter's sentencing that the
OL,9,Fearlier referral had been made to
OL,10,Fcounter terrorism officers.
OL,12,F"I mean we could have stopped her, we
OL,13,Fcould have made sure this didn't
OL,14,Fhappen," he said.
OL,16,F"For that information not to be
OL,17,Freleased to us in May, that is a
OL,18,Fsignificant failure. But that could
OL,19,Fhave been released in June or July.
OL,26,@nD@VOUnD@^O]tD@AOUvD@HO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,F"The laptop she was using was a
OL,7,FChristmas present that year. If we
OL,8,Fwere aware that she was using that
OL,9,Finappropriately, then obviously we
OL,10,Fcould have somehow restricted her.
OL,12,F"We could have intervened, we could
OL,13,Fhave had conversations with her. There
OL,14,Fwas no reason why she would not have
OL,15,Flistened to us."
OL,17,FCCTV footage shows Burns in a fast-
OL,18,Ffood restaurant in the hours before
OL,19,Fthe attack.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,FBurns attacked Mr Mahmoodi with the
OL,7,Faxe as he stood outside a barber's
OL,8,Fshop in East Street, Bedminster,
OL,9,FBristol in August last year, causing a
OL,10,Fsmall wound to his neck.
OL,12,FThat morning her parents had reported
OL,13,Fher missing to police because they had
OL,14,Fbecome concerned for her welfare and
OL,15,Fshe was not answering her mother's
OL,16,Fmobile phone that she had borrowed.
OL,18,FThey feared it could be the latest in
OL,19,Fa series of self-harming incidents.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,FIn the May she had been taken into
OL,7,Fcustody by police because of fears for
OL,8,Fher welfare but after a mental health
OL,9,Fassessment was taken home to her
OL,10,Fparents, who are both teachers.
OL,12,F"People should not be released back to
OL,13,Fthe family without a proper care
OL,14,Fplan," he said.
OL,16,F"If somebody has attempted to take
OL,17,Ftheir life there has to be dedicated
OL,18,Fteams involved to make sure that
OL,19,Fperson is safe.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@FO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,F"You cannot just return them to the
OL,7,Fhome and literally say, your
OL,8,Fresponsibility."
OL,10,FMr Burns has made two complaints to
OL,11,Fthe police regarding his daughter's
OL,12,Fcase relating to her release from
OL,13,Fcustody in May, and the second about
OL,14,Fthe referral to Counter Terrorism
OL,15,FPolicing.
OL,17,F"Alina's GP made it very clear that
OL,18,Fthey were not happy that no referral
OL,19,Fwas made to them," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@PO]yD@AOU{D@RO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,F"They felt there had been a misstep in
OL,7,Fhelping her. There should have been a
OL,8,Fcare plan in place and she should not
OL,9,Fhave just been brought home.
OL,11,F"Counter Terrorism Policing were aware
OL,12,Fof concerns that they had received a
OL,13,Freferral from Avon and Somerset Police
OL,14,Fin March 2025 and they considered it
OL,15,Fdid not meet the threshold and
OL,16,Freferred it back to Avon and Somerset.
OL,18,F"That was two months before the May
OL,19,Fincident. They were aware there was an
OL,20,Fon-going issue ` they should have
OL,21,Finformed us."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,FBurns remained silent during this
OL,7,Finterview with police.
OL,9,FBurns, of Bristol, pleaded guilty to
OL,10,Fattempted murder and three charges of
OL,11,Fhaving an article with a blade or
OL,12,Fpoint ` specifically an axe, a scalpel
OL,13,Fand two darts.
OL,15,FThe sentencing judge imposed a
OL,16,Fcustodial sentence of 15-and-a-half
OL,17,Fyears and an additional four-year
OL,18,Fperiod on licence.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,FAn Avon and Somerset Police spokesman
OL,7,Fsaid: "We received a formal complaint
OL,8,Ffrom the family of Alina Burns in
OL,9,Frelation to a concern for safety-
OL,10,Frelated incident in Bedminster in May
OL,11,F2025.
OL,13,F"Following a thorough investigation by
OL,14,Four professional standards department
OL,15,Finto the actions we took, it was
OL,16,Fdetermined that advice was sought from
OL,17,Fmental health professionals,
OL,18,Fappropriate safeguarding risk
OL,19,Fassessments were completed and all
OL,20,Frelevant policies and procedures were
OL,21,Ffollowed.
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,F"The service provided by the police in
OL,7,Fthis case was deemed to be acceptable."
OL,9,FThe force said it was assessing a
OL,10,Ffurther complaint from the family
OL,11,Fregarding the counter terrorism
OL,12,Freferral.
OL,14,F"We will keep the complainant updated
OL,15,Fon the progress of the assessment and
OL,16,Fany subsequent investigation," they
OL,17,Fadded.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@gO]vD@AOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43918
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,FA Counter Terrorism Policing South
OL,7,FWest spokeswoman said: "We can confirm
OL,8,Fthat CTP South West received
OL,9,Finformation relating to messages that
OL,10,FBurns had sent to another individual
OL,11,Fon a messaging platform.
OL,13,F"Those messages were assessed by
OL,14,Fspecialist officers, and it was found
OL,15,Fthat no further action was to be taken
OL,16,Fby CTP and these were passed to the
OL,17,Flocal force for safeguarding purposes.
OL,26,@oD@XOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G18/19
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
