OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43919
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780751474
OL,3,CFather of jailed far-right extremist
OL,4,Csays agencies failed teenage daughter
OL,6,F"Since the awful attack on the August
OL,7,F2, we have conducted a thorough review
OL,8,Fof the decision-making related to
OL,9,Fthose messages and learning has been
OL,10,Fidentified."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G19/19
